WEBVTT

00:01:28.994 --> 00:01:32.810
Alem din „Refugiatul” de Benjamin Zephaniah;

00:01:32.810 --> 00:01:35.394
Luke Skywalker,

00:01:35.394 --> 00:01:38.265
Luke Skywalker! (Râsete)

00:01:38.265 --> 00:01:40.552
Oliver Twist;

00:01:40.552 --> 00:01:44.763
Cassia, din „Concubina din Shangai” de Hong Ying;

00:01:44.763 --> 00:01:48.120
Celie, din „Culoarea violet” de Alice Walker.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:52.732
Toate aceste mari personaje,

00:01:52.732 --> 00:01:56.729
